    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p> 今天继续鼓捣虚拟机。记录一下用到的东西：</p><p> 分辨率设置：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">xrandr --output Virtual1 --mode &quot;1920x1200&quot;</span><br><span class="line">xrandr -m #获得显示器名称 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Launcher <code>rofi</code>:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bindsym $mod+d exec rofi -show drun</span><br><span class="line">bindsym $mod+d exec rofi -show window</span><br><span class="line"># 绑定两个快捷键就可以 </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Get rid of the titlebar:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">new_window none</span><br><span class="line">new_float normal</span><br><span class="line">hide_edge_borders both</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Customize the statusbar:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cp &#x2F;etc&#x2F;i3status.conf ~&#x2F;.config&#x2F;i3status&#x2F;config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Done.</p><p> 参考到的文章有：</p><ul><li><a href="https://mchladek.me/post/arch-mbp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Installing Arch Linux on a MacBook Pro</a></li><li><a href="http://codylittlewood.com/arch-linux-on-macbook-pro-installation/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Dual boot Arch Linux on MacBook Pro Installation</a></li><li><a href="https://blog.gimo.me/post/from-macos-to-archlinux/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> 从 macOS 到 Arch Linux</a></li></ul>]]></content>
    
