  <entry>
    <title>VirtualBox 安装 Archlinux 指南</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/02/26/xx026/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/02/26/xx026/</id>
    <published>2020-02-26T09:06:39.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-02-26T15:40:44.538Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>最近无聊，就找来 <code>archlinux</code> 在虚拟机玩。去 <a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Installation_guide" target="_blank" rel="noopener">archlinux wiki</a> 上看了一下教程。以下是操作过程：</p><h2 id="安装基础系统"><a href="# 安装基础系统" class="headerlink" title="安装基础系统"></a>安装基础系统 </h2><p> 下载镜像，放到光驱，光驱启动。联网，测试连接。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # dhcpcd</span><br><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # ping archlinux.org -c 4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更新系统时间：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # timedatectl set-ntp true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>磁盘分区并格式化：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # fdisk -l</span><br><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # fdisk &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运用 fdisk 对硬盘进行分区，因为只是自己玩，在这里就只分三个分区，第一个为 boot 启动分区(200M)，第二个为 swap 交换分区(2G)，第三个作为系统盘(剩余的空间)。分区创建完成后进行格式化。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # mkfs.ext4 &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda1</span><br><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # mkfs.ext4 &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda3</span><br><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # mkswap &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda2</span><br><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # swapon &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>挂载分区：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # mount &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda3 &#x2F;mnt</span><br><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # mkdir &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;boot</span><br><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # mount &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda1 &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;boot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改软件源并更新：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # vi &#x2F;etc&#x2F;pacman.d&#x2F;mirrorlist</span><br><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # pacman -Sy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将中国的源放在问文件最前面，个人觉得中科大 (ustc) 和 163 的源比较好。<br>安装系统到磁盘：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # pacstrap &#x2F;mnt base linux linux-firmware</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="配置基本系统"><a href="# 配置基本系统" class="headerlink" title="配置基本系统"></a>配置基本系统 </h2><p> 将分区表写入系统配置文件：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # genfstab -U &#x2F;mnt &gt;&gt; &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;etc&#x2F;fstab</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入磁盘系统：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@mxarch ~ # arch-chroot &#x2F;mnt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置时区：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# ln -sf &#x2F;usr&#x2F;share&#x2F;zoneinfo&#x2F;Asia&#x2F;Shanghai &#x2F;etc&#x2F;localtime</span><br><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# hwclock --systohc --utc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置语言：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# vi &#x2F;etc&#x2F;locale.gen</span><br><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# locale-gen</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将你需要的语言格式的注释去掉，默认是全部注释。<br>配置主机名并配置网络，建议安装 NetworkManager，并用 <code>systemctl start/enable</code> 启动服务。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># systemctl disable dhcpcd.service</span><br><span class="line"># systemctl enable NetworkManager.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置 root 密码并添加普通用户：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# passwd</span><br><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# useradd -m 用户名</span><br><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# passwd 用户名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装引导程序：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# pacman -S grub</span><br><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# grub-install --target&#x3D;i386-pc --recheck &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda</span><br><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# grub-mkconfig -o &#x2F;boot&#x2F;grub&#x2F;grub.cfg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完成安装</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# exit</span><br><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# umount -R &#x2F;mnt</span><br><span class="line">[root@mxarch &#x2F;]# poweroff</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将 iso 镜像移除重新启动 <code>archlinux</code>。</p><h2 id="安装桌面环境"><a href="# 安装桌面环境" class="headerlink" title="安装桌面环境"></a>安装桌面环境 </h2><p> 安装显卡驱动：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># pacman -S virtualbox-guest-utils #虚拟机</span><br><span class="line"># pacman -S xf86-video-intel mesa-libgl libva-intel-driver libva</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装 xorg：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@mxarch ~]# pacman -S xorg-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装桌面环境：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@mxarch ~]# pacman -S xfce4 xfce4-goodies</span><br><span class="line">[root@mxarch ~]# pacman -S lightdm lightdm-gtk-greeter</span><br><span class="line">[root@mxarch ~]# systemctl enable lightdm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="中文相关问题"><a href="# 中文相关问题" class="headerlink" title="中文相关问题"></a>中文相关问题 </h2><p> 中文乱码一般都是因为没有中文字体：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S wqy-zenhei ttf-fireflysung</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>中文输入法 <br> 修改配置文件，<code>~/.xinitrc</code> or <code>~/.xprofile</code>加入以下内容：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export GTK_IM_MODULE&#x3D;fcitx</span><br><span class="line">export QT_IM_MODULE&#x3D;fcitx</span><br><span class="line">export XMODIFIERS&#x3D;&quot;@im&#x3D;fcitx&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完成。</p><h2 id="结论"><a href="# 结论" class="headerlink" title="结论"></a>结论 </h2><p> 安装之后的推荐设置可以参考 <a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/General_recommendations" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> 官方文档 </a>。<br> 测试下来的话，表现最好的桌面环境是，<code>Cinnamon</code>，or <code>Xfce</code>，or <code>awesome</code>。另外新系统是最小系统，所以如果要编译东西的话，需要提前安装，<code>make</code>, <code>gcc</code>, <code>sudo</code>, <code>fakeroot</code>等。</p><p>PS.</p><ul><li>HiDPI 的支持，需要安装 <code>xrandr</code>。然后把 <code>xrandr --dpi 192</code> 这条命令加入开机启动项。</li><li>安装一些额外的字体使用下面的命令：</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># pacman -S ttf-dejavu ttf-droid ttf-fira-mono ttf-fira-sans ttf-liberation ttf-linux-libertine-g ttf-oxygen ttf-tlwg ttf-ubuntu-font-family</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>如果 <code>sudoer</code> 错误出现，在 <code>：$vim /etc/sudoers</code> 中加入当前用户即可。</li><li><code>zsh</code> 切换使用命令 <code>chsh -s /bin/zsh</code>, if not sure, check where zsh is by <code>which zsh</code> .</li></ul>]]></content>
    
